<title>jlst kạlʿạdẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jlst kạlʿạdẗ lrbhạ bạtḍạʿ tfkr fy ywmhạ wkyf mḍy̱
 wtsẖkr ạ̹lhhạ lmạ ḥdtẖ lhạ wtṭlbh strạaⁿ lhạ fy gẖdhạ
 slạm lk ạ̉ythạ ạlmnʿm ʿlyhạ
 slạm lk mbạrkẗ ạ̉nt fy ạlnsạʾ
 stḥblyn wtldyn ạ̉bnạaⁿ tsmyh yswʿ
 ạ̉bn ạlʿly ykwn ʿẓymạaⁿ mlkh krsy̱ dạwd
 fqạlt mrym llmlạk : kyf ykwn hdẖạ wạ̉nạ lst ạ̉ʿrf rjlạaⁿ
 rwḥh ạlqdws yḥl ʿlyk wqwth tẓllk
 fạlqdws ạlmwlwd mnk ydʿy̱ ạ̉bn ạllh</lyrics>
</song>